          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">The price is based on the average price of four postings by a trading company on Alibaba.com (accessed on 2022-09-11). 
The price was converted from USD to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2022-02-15) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=sts_inpp_a&amp;lang=en, last accessed on 2022-05-04).</comment>
        </property>
